{"title":"跋涉者","authors":["曹增书"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":9,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"跋涉者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曹增书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听见驼铃在歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱着走出荒漠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见他跪在花的原野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掬饮甘泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一排年轻的红柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在早霞里沉思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红红的接力棒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在绿洲上传递"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那上面有血的气息，汗的气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河静静淌着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布谷声声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水渐渐清澈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着曲曲折折的海岸线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走来了十四位英俊的少年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们互相凝视了一会儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始弄潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是在子夜里出发的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陪伴他的，是无数战斗的诗魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一边走，一边倾听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他深知，只有从泥土汲取灵感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能永葆童心"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}